Author: junebug-2019
Text: I do taekwondo and I have to eat 30 minutes before workout and right after.  My masters also know about my ED so they won't let me push as hard and make sure I eat afterwards

Author: EzraCelestine
Text: Depending on how comfortable you are with your instructors, maybe you could ask them to keep an eye on you so you don't overdo things? You don't have to mention the ED; just say some bullshit about accidentally pushing too hard and getting a minor injury in the past or smth
